                <h1>Can You Use Wallpaper in the Bathroom? Tips and Ideas</h1>
                <p>Yes, you can put wallpaper in the bathroom, but it requires special consideration. Choose moisture-resistant, washable wallpaper to prevent damage from humidity and steam. Vinyl coatings or backed wallpapers are ideal for this environment. Proper installation and ventilation will also help maintain the wallpaper's longevity.</p>
